#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.81"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.81:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.81:0.2"
msgid "8. Khajjanīyavagga"
msgstr "8. Itchy"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 81. Pālileyyasutta → pārileyyakasuttaṃ (bj) | pārileyya (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.81:0.3"
msgid "81. Pālileyyasutta"
msgstr "81. At Pārileyya"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.95"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery."

msgctxt "sn22.81:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya kosambiṃ "
"piṇḍāya pāvisi."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, "
"entered Kosambi for alms."

msgctxt "sn22.81:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kosambiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto sāmaṃ senāsanaṃ "
"saṃsāmetvā pattacīvaramādāya anāmantetvā upaṭṭhāke anapaloketvā "
"bhikkhusaṃghaṃ eko adutiyo cārikaṃ pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"After the meal, on his return from alms-round, he set his lodgings in order "
"himself. Taking his bowl and robe, without informing his attendants or "
"taking leave of the mendicant Saṅgha, he set out to go wandering alone, with "
"no companion."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu acirapakkantassa bhagavato yenāyasmā ānando "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then, not long after the Buddha had left, one of the mendicants went to "
"Venerable Ānanda and told him what had happened."

msgctxt "sn22.81:2.2"
msgid ""
"“esāvuso ānanda, bhagavā sāmaṃ senāsanaṃ saṃsāmetvā pattacīvaramādāya "
"anāmantetvā upaṭṭhāke anapaloketvā bhikkhusaṅghaṃ eko adutiyo cārikaṃ "
"pakkanto”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:2.3"
msgid ""
"“Yasmiṃ, āvuso, samaye bhagavā sāmaṃ senāsanaṃ saṃsāmetvā pattacīvaramādāya "
"anāmantetvā upaṭṭhāke anapaloketvā bhikkhusaṅghaṃ eko adutiyo cārikaṃ "
"pakkamati, ekova bhagavā tasmiṃ samaye viharitukāmo hoti;"
msgstr ""
"Ānanda said: “Reverend, when the Buddha leaves like this it means he wants "
"to stay alone."

msgctxt "sn22.81:2.4"
msgid "na bhagavā tasmiṃ samaye kenaci anubandhitabbo hotī”ti."
msgstr "At this time no-one should follow him.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: pālileyyakaṃ → pārileyyakaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.81:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā anupubbena cārikaṃ caramāno yena pālileyyakaṃ tadavasari."
msgstr "Then the Buddha, traveling stage by stage, arrived at Pārileyya,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:3.2"
msgid "Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā pālileyyake viharati bhaddasālamūle."
msgstr "where he stayed at the root of a sacred sal tree."

msgctxt "sn22.81:3.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"āyasmatā ānandena saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"Then several mendicants went up to Venerable Ānanda and exchanged greetings "
"with him."

msgctxt "sn22.81:3.4"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinnā kho te bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, they sat down to one "
"side and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn22.81:3.5"
msgid "“cirassutā kho no, āvuso ānanda, bhagavato sammukhā dhammī kathā;"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, it’s been a long time since we’ve heard a Dhamma talk from the "
"Buddha."

msgctxt "sn22.81:3.6"
msgid ""
"icchāma mayaṃ, āvuso ānanda, bhagavato sammukhā dhammiṃ kathaṃ sotun”ti."
msgstr "We wish to hear a Dhamma talk from the Buddha.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.96"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando tehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ yena pālileyyakaṃ "
"bhaddasālamūlaṃ yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda together with those mendicants went to Pārileyya to "
"see the Buddha. They bowed and sat down to one side,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.2"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ nisinne kho te bhikkhū bhagavā dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi "
"samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi."
msgstr ""
"and the Buddha educated, encouraged, fired up, and inspired them with a "
"Dhamma talk."

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa bhikkhuno evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi:"
msgstr "Now at that time one of the monks had the thought:"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.4"
msgid "“kathaṃ nu kho jānato kathaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hotī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“How do you know and see in order to end the defilements in the present "
"life?”"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā tassa bhikkhuno cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya bhikkhū "
"āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha, knowing what that monk was thinking, addressed the "
"mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.6"
msgid "“vicayaso desito, bhikkhave, mayā dhammo;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, I’ve taught the Dhamma analytically."

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.7"
msgid "vicayaso desitā cattāro satipaṭṭhānā;"
msgstr "I’ve analytically taught the four kinds of mindfulness meditation,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.8"
msgid "vicayaso desitā cattāro sammappadhānā;"
msgstr "the four right efforts,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.9"
msgid "vicayaso desitā cattāro iddhipādā;"
msgstr "the four bases of psychic power,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.10"
msgid "vicayaso desitāni pañcindriyāni;"
msgstr "the five faculties,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.11"
msgid "vicayaso desitāni pañca balāni;"
msgstr "the five powers,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.12"
msgid "vicayaso desitā sattabojjhaṅgā;"
msgstr "the seven awakening factors,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.13"
msgid "vicayaso desito ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo."
msgstr "and the noble eightfold path."

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.14"
msgid "Evaṃ vicayaso desito, bhikkhave, mayā dhammo."
msgstr "That’s how I’ve taught the Dhamma analytically."

# Contra BB, I read this as a locative absolute. The context, and the panidhekaccassa, suggest the sense of “though, despite”. It seems a bit harsh, but I guess the Buddha was in a bad mood. Unless we take this sense, the structure of the Buddha’s answer is hard to account for.
msgctxt "sn22.81:4.15"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vicayaso desite kho, bhikkhave, mayā dhamme atha ca panidhekaccassa "
"bhikkhuno evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"Though I’ve taught the Dhamma analytically, still a certain mendicant "
"present here has this thought:"

msgctxt "sn22.81:4.16"
msgid "‘kathaṃ nu kho jānato kathaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hotī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘How do you know and see in order to end the defilements in the present "
"life?’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.97"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:5.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, jānato kathaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hoti?"
msgstr ""
"And how, mendicants, do you know and see in order to end the defilements in "
"the present life?"

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha bhikkhave, assutavā puthujjano ariyānaṃ adassāvī ariyadhammassa akovido "
"ariyadhamme avinīto, sappurisānaṃ adassāvī sappurisadhammassa akovido "
"sappurisadhamme avinīto "
msgstr ""
"Take an uneducated ordinary person who has not seen the noble ones, and is "
"neither skilled nor trained in the teaching of the noble ones. They’ve not "
"seen good persons, and are neither skilled nor trained in the teaching of "
"the good persons. "

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.3"
msgid "rūpaṃ attato samanupassati."
msgstr "They regard form as self."

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.4"
msgid "Yā kho pana sā, bhikkhave, samanupassanā saṅkhāro so."
msgstr "But that regarding is just a conditioned phenomenon."

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.5"
msgid "So pana saṅkhāro kiṃnidāno kiṃsamudayo kiṃjātiko kiṃpabhavo?"
msgstr ""
"And what’s the source, origin, birthplace, and root of that conditioned "
"phenomenon?"

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.6"
msgid ""
"Avijjāsamphassajena, bhikkhave, vedayitena phuṭṭhassa assutavato "
"puthujjanassa uppannā taṇhā;"
msgstr ""
"When an uneducated ordinary person is struck by feelings born of contact "
"with ignorance, craving arises."

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.7"
msgid "tatojo so saṅkhāro."
msgstr "That conditioned phenomenon is born from that."

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.8"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, sopi saṅkhāro anicco saṅkhato paṭiccasamuppanno."
msgstr ""
"So that conditioned phenomenon is impermanent, conditioned, and dependently "
"originated."

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.9"
msgid "Sāpi taṇhā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā."
msgstr "And that craving,"

# The syntax here suggests that vedana and phassa are to be taken together. But the later passages show that this is just an artifact of abbreviation.
msgctxt "sn22.81:5.10"
msgid "Sāpi vedanā, sopi phasso anicco saṅkhato paṭiccasamuppanno."
msgstr "that feeling, that contact,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.11"
msgid "Sāpi avijjā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā."
msgstr ""
"and that ignorance are also impermanent, conditioned, and dependently "
"originated."

msgctxt "sn22.81:5.12"
msgid ""
"Evampi kho, bhikkhave, jānato evaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hoti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how you should know and see in order to end the defilements in the "
"present life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:6.1"
msgid "Na heva kho rūpaṃ attato samanupassati;"
msgstr "Perhaps they don’t regard form as self,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.2"
msgid "api ca kho rūpavantaṃ attānaṃ samanupassati."
msgstr "but they still regard self as possessing form."

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.3"
msgid "Yā kho pana sā, bhikkhave, samanupassanā saṅkhāro so."
msgstr "But that regarding is just a conditioned phenomenon. …"

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.4"
msgid "So pana saṅkhāro kiṃnidāno kiṃsamudayo kiṃjātiko kiṃpabhavo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.5"
msgid ""
"Avijjāsamphassajena, bhikkhave, vedayitena phuṭṭhassa assutavato "
"puthujjanassa uppannā taṇhā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.6"
msgid "tatojo so saṅkhāro."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.7"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, sopi saṅkhāro anicco saṅkhato paṭiccasamuppanno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.8"
msgid "Sāpi taṇhā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.9"
msgid "sāpi vedanā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.10"
msgid "sopi phasso …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.11"
msgid "sāpi avijjā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:6.12"
msgid ""
"Evampi kho, bhikkhave, jānato evaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:7.1"
msgid ""
"Na heva kho rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ attānaṃ samanupassati;"
msgstr "Perhaps they don’t regard form as self, or self as possessing form,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.2"
msgid "api ca kho attani rūpaṃ samanupassati."
msgstr "but they still regard form in self."

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.3"
msgid "Yā kho pana sā, bhikkhave, samanupassanā saṅkhāro so."
msgstr "But that regarding is just a conditioned phenomenon. …"

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.4"
msgid "So pana saṅkhāro kiṃnidāno kiṃsamudayo kiṃjātiko kiṃpabhavo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.5"
msgid ""
"Avijjāsamphassajena, bhikkhave, vedayitena phuṭṭhassa assutavato "
"puthujjanassa uppannā taṇhā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.6"
msgid "tatojo so saṅkhāro."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.7"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, sopi saṅkhāro anicco saṅkhato paṭiccasamuppanno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.8"
msgid "Sāpi taṇhā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.9"
msgid "sāpi vedanā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.10"
msgid "sopi phasso …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.11"
msgid "sāpi avijjā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:7.12"
msgid ""
"Evampi kho, bhikkhave, jānato evaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.98"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:8.1"
msgid ""
"Na heva kho rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ attānaṃ samanupassati, "
"na attani rūpaṃ samanupassati;"
msgstr ""
"Perhaps they don’t regard form as self, or self as possessing form, or form "
"in self,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.2"
msgid "api ca kho rūpasmiṃ attānaṃ samanupassati."
msgstr "but they still regard self in form."

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.3"
msgid "Yā kho pana sā, bhikkhave, samanupassanā saṅkhāro so."
msgstr "But that regarding is just a conditioned phenomenon. …"

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.4"
msgid "So pana saṅkhāro kiṃnidāno kiṃsamudayo kiṃjātiko kiṃpabhavo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.5"
msgid ""
"Avijjāsamphassajena, bhikkhave, vedayitena phuṭṭhassa assutavato "
"puthujjanassa uppannā taṇhā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.6"
msgid "tatojo so saṅkhāro."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.7"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, sopi saṅkhāro anicco saṅkhato paṭiccasamuppanno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.8"
msgid "Sāpi taṇhā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.9"
msgid "sāpi vedanā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.10"
msgid "sopi phasso …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.11"
msgid "sāpi avijjā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:8.12"
msgid "Evampi kho, bhikkhave, jānato … pe … āsavānaṃ khayo hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:9.1"
msgid ""
"Na heva kho rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ attānaṃ, na attani "
"rūpaṃ, na rūpasmiṃ attānaṃ samanupassati;"
msgstr ""
"Perhaps they don’t regard form as self, or self as possessing form, or form "
"in self, or self in form."

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.2"
msgid ""
"api ca kho vedanaṃ attato samanupassati, api ca kho vedanāvantaṃ attānaṃ "
"samanupassati, api ca kho attani vedanaṃ samanupassati, api ca kho vedanāya "
"attānaṃ samanupassati;"
msgstr "But they regard feeling as self …"

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.3"
msgid "api ca kho saññaṃ …"
msgstr "perception as self …"

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.4"
msgid ""
"api ca kho saṅkhāre attato samanupassati, api ca kho saṅkhāravantaṃ attānaṃ "
"samanupassati, api ca kho attani saṅkhāre samanupassati, api ca kho "
"saṅkhāresu attānaṃ samanupassati;"
msgstr "choices as self …"

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.5"
msgid ""
"api ca kho viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, api ca kho viññāṇavantaṃ attānaṃ, "
"api ca kho attani viññāṇaṃ, api ca kho viññāṇasmiṃ attānaṃ samanupassati."
msgstr "consciousness as self …"

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.6"
msgid "Yā kho pana sā, bhikkhave, samanupassanā saṅkhāro so."
msgstr "But that regarding is just a conditioned phenomenon."

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.7"
msgid "So pana saṅkhāro kiṃnidāno … pe … kiṃpabhavo?"
msgstr "And what’s the source of that conditioned phenomenon?"

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.8"
msgid ""
"Avijjāsamphassajena, bhikkhave, vedayitena phuṭṭhassa assutavato "
"puthujjanassa uppannā taṇhā;"
msgstr ""
"When an uneducated ordinary person is struck by feelings born of contact "
"with ignorance, craving arises."

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.9"
msgid "tatojo so saṅkhāro."
msgstr "That conditioned phenomenon is born from that."

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.10"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, sopi saṅkhāro anicco saṅkhato paṭiccasamuppanno."
msgstr ""
"So that conditioned phenomenon is impermanent, conditioned, and dependently "
"originated."

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.11"
msgid "Sāpi taṇhā …"
msgstr "And that craving,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.12"
msgid "sāpi vedanā …"
msgstr "that feeling,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.13"
msgid "sopi phasso …"
msgstr "that contact,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.14"
msgid "sāpi avijjā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā."
msgstr ""
"and that ignorance are also impermanent, conditioned, and dependently "
"originated."

msgctxt "sn22.81:9.15"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, jānato evaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hoti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how you should know and see in order to end the defilements in the "
"present life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:10.1"
msgid "Na heva kho rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, "
msgstr "Perhaps they don’t regard form "

msgctxt "sn22.81:10.2"
msgid "na vedanaṃ attato samanupassati, "
msgstr "or feeling "

msgctxt "sn22.81:10.3"
msgid "na saññaṃ …"
msgstr "or perception"

msgctxt "sn22.81:10.4"
msgid "na saṅkhāre …"
msgstr "or choices"

msgctxt "sn22.81:10.5"
msgid "na viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati;"
msgstr "or consciousness as self."

msgctxt "sn22.81:10.6"
msgid "api ca kho evaṃdiṭṭhi hoti:"
msgstr "Still, they have such a view:"

# This kind of double demonstrative construction is an emphatic identity. This is in fact the Upanishadic thesis.
msgctxt "sn22.81:10.7"
msgid ""
"‘so attā so loko, so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato "
"avipariṇāmadhammo’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The self and the cosmos are one and the same. After passing away I will be "
"permanent, everlasting, eternal, and imperishable.’"

msgctxt "sn22.81:10.8"
msgid "Yā kho pana sā, bhikkhave, sassatadiṭṭhi saṅkhāro so."
msgstr "But that eternalist view is just a conditioned phenomenon."

msgctxt "sn22.81:10.9"
msgid "So pana saṅkhāro kiṃnidāno … pe …"
msgstr "And what’s the source of that conditioned phenomenon? …"

msgctxt "sn22.81:10.10"
msgid ""
"evampi kho, bhikkhave, jānato evaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hoti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how you should know and see in order to end the defilements in the "
"present life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.99"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:11.1"
msgid "Na heva kho rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, "
msgstr "Perhaps they don’t regard form "

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.2"
msgid "na vedanaṃ …"
msgstr "or feeling"

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.3"
msgid "na saññaṃ …"
msgstr "or perception"

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.4"
msgid "na saṅkhāre …"
msgstr "or choices"

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.5"
msgid "na viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati;"
msgstr "or consciousness as self."

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.6"
msgid "nāpi evaṃdiṭṭhi hoti:"
msgstr "Nor do they have such a view:"

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.7"
msgid ""
"‘so attā so loko, so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato "
"avipariṇāmadhammo’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The self and the cosmos are one and the same. After passing away I will be "
"permanent, everlasting, eternal, and imperishable.’"

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.8"
msgid "Api ca kho evaṃdiṭṭhi hoti:"
msgstr "Still, they have such a view:"

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.9"
msgid "‘no cassaṃ no ca me siyā nābhavissaṃ na me bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I might not be, and it might not be mine. I will not be, and it will not be "
"mine.’"

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.10"
msgid "Yā kho pana sā, bhikkhave, ucchedadiṭṭhi saṅkhāro so."
msgstr "But that annihilationist view is just a conditioned phenomenon."

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.11"
msgid "So pana saṅkhāro kiṃnidāno kiṃsamudayo kiṃjātiko kiṃpabhavo?"
msgstr "And what’s the source of that conditioned phenomenon? …"

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.12"
msgid ""
"Avijjāsamphassajena, bhikkhave, vedayitena phuṭṭhassa assutavato "
"puthujjanassa uppannā taṇhā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.13"
msgid "tatojo so saṅkhāro."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.14"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, sopi saṅkhāro anicco … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.81:11.15"
msgid ""
"evampi kho, bhikkhave, jānato evaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hoti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how you should know and see in order to end the defilements in the "
"present life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.81:12.1"
msgid "Na heva kho rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, na vedanaṃ …"
msgstr "Perhaps they don’t regard form or feeling"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.2"
msgid "na saññaṃ …"
msgstr "or perception"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.3"
msgid "na saṅkhāre …"
msgstr "or choices"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.4"
msgid "na viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati … pe …"
msgstr "or consciousness as self."

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.5"
msgid "na viññāṇasmiṃ attato samanupassati, nāpi evaṃdiṭṭhi hoti:"
msgstr "Nor do they have such a view:"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.6"
msgid ""
"‘so attā so loko, so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato "
"avipariṇāmadhammo’ti;"
msgstr ""
"‘The self and the cosmos are one and the same. After passing away I will be "
"permanent, everlasting, eternal, and imperishable.’"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.7"
msgid "nāpi evaṃdiṭṭhi hoti:"
msgstr "Nor do they have such a view:"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.8"
msgid "‘no cassaṃ no ca me siyā nābhavissaṃ na me bhavissatī’ti;"
msgstr ""
"‘I might not be, and it might not be mine. I will not be, and it will not be "
"mine.’"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.9"
msgid "api ca kho kaṅkhī hoti vicikicchī aniṭṭhaṅgato saddhamme."
msgstr ""
"Still, they have doubts and uncertainties. They’re undecided about the true "
"teaching."

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.10"
msgid ""
"Yā kho pana sā, bhikkhave, kaṅkhitā vicikicchitā aniṭṭhaṅgatatā saddhamme "
"saṅkhāro so."
msgstr ""
"That doubt and uncertainty, the indecision about the true teaching, is just "
"a conditioned phenomenon."

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.11"
msgid "So pana saṅkhāro kiṃnidāno kiṃsamudayo kiṃjātiko kiṃpabhavo?"
msgstr "And what’s the source of that conditioned phenomenon?"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.12"
msgid ""
"Avijjāsamphassajena, bhikkhave, vedayitena phuṭṭhassa assutavato "
"puthujjanassa uppannā taṇhā;"
msgstr ""
"When an uneducated ordinary person is struck by feelings born of contact "
"with ignorance, craving arises."

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.13"
msgid "tatojo so saṅkhāro."
msgstr "That conditioned phenomenon is born from that."

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.14"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, sopi saṅkhāro anicco saṅkhato paṭiccasamuppanno."
msgstr ""
"So that conditioned phenomenon is impermanent, conditioned, and dependently "
"originated."

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.15"
msgid "Sāpi taṇhā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā."
msgstr "And that craving,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.16"
msgid "Sāpi vedanā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā."
msgstr "that feeling,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.17"
msgid "Sopi phasso anicco saṅkhato paṭiccasamuppanno."
msgstr "that contact,"

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.18"
msgid "Sāpi avijjā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā."
msgstr ""
"and that ignorance are also impermanent, conditioned, and dependently "
"originated."

msgctxt "sn22.81:12.19"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, jānato evaṃ passato anantarā āsavānaṃ khayo hotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how you should know and see in order to end the defilements in the "
"present life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.81:12.20"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
